==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Talebearing
<hw>Tale"bear`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of informing
officiously; communication of secrets, scandal, etc.,
maliciously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

